Subject: [PATCH] mt76: mt7921: do not schedule hw reset if the device is not
 running
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 5.13.2
Git-commit: d74c4b5667425c35d74906795a08e02e29df5b46

[ Upstream commit d74c4b5667425c35d74906795a08e02e29df5b46 ]

